{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"276469-it-s-all-the-cat-s-fault","title":"Tout Sa Se Fòt Chat la!","description":"Ti gason nan istwa sa a pa t kapab fin fè devwa l poutèt yon vye chat malfezan. Sa sanble ak yon eskiz raz, pa vre? Ebyen, li pou konnen kisa ki te pase l, epi w ap wè kijan yon sèl bagay ka mennen nan yon lòt, epi nan yon lòt, epi nan yon lòt...","language":"Haitian Creole","langCode":"ht","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Danielle M. Josyle"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/276469-it-s-all-the-cat-s-fault"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size3/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/696669/size6/8717a72070ac52bd090aeebc8e6b36e6.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13955/size6/74b224ec7927eb345bdc2c97d734e290.jpg","text":"Poukisa ou pa t fè devwa w? \nMetrès, tout sa se fòt chat la.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13956/size6/cd8835c2cbb54badb351efe4519e3c73.jpg","text":"Si li pa t koke nan pyebwa a, mwen pa t ap al pran nechèl la pou m monte l.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13957/size6/82dcc28b0ebb8f0b4d44834aefe31da9.jpg","text":"Si mwen pa t al pran nechèl la pou m monte l, mwen pa t ap bezwen ranje l.\nSi mwen pa t bezwen ranje l, mwen pa t ap reveye ti bebe a.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13958/size6/cbebcafd09ccafb93a53ccbf97d5212d.jpg","text":"Si mwen pa t reveye ti bebe a, manman m pa t ap kouri sòti nan kuizin nan.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13959/size6/6afe4b32d72fda92b47269657fdd7f5e.jpg","text":"Si makak la pa t antre, li pa t ap manje tout manje a.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13960/size6/47a620ff87a41f00183aa5c5d6ef823d.jpg","text":"Si papa m pa t achte woti ak poul curry nan magazen te a, chen an pa t ap suiv li lakay la.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13961/size6/46fe6dae5591c1691562f296e5ec8e86.jpg","text":"Si chen an pa t suiv li lakay la, li pa t ap manje devwa m nan.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13962/size6/5859bccb9c8b5fd5f6d2056c1ebeb45c.jpg","text":"Ebyen, ou vle fè m konprann ke chen an manje devwa w la?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/13965/size6/50392cc21b95981389adaae52caf3f30.jpg","text":"Wi, Metrès, tout sa se fòt chat la!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":9,"words":161}}